&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Division of Medicine and Urgent care &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Gastroenterology, Endoscopy &amp; Respiratory Medicine&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An excellent opportunity has arisen for a dynamic, innovative and highly motivated Manager to join our team as Directorate Manager for the Gastroenterology and Respiratory services at Northampton General Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be an integral member of the senior team within the Division and Directorate, working closely with the Clinical Director and Matrons in General medicine to manage these busy dynamic services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be responsible for the management of all key national targets so a good understand of these is essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are proud to be the first hospital in the UK to have obtained Pathway to Excellence® designated accreditation from the American nurses credentialing centre (ANCC). We have also been rated as a GOOD hospital in our most recent CQC inspection and hope you will join us on our journey to becoming OUTSTANDING.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We celebrate staff achievements and value the importance of working as one big team. That’s why we talk about TeamNGH. It’s all about working together to provide the best possible care for our patients and supporting each other to grow and develop our skills. At NGH we are driven to helping you to be the best you can be.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Interviews are scheduled for the week commencing 16th November 2020&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Catherine Briers Job title: Divisional Manager/Directorate Manager Email address: catherine.briers@ngh.nhs.uk Telephone number: 01604523313&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mary Visser - Divisional Manager for Medicine &amp; Urgent care 01604 525286.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;e-mail: mary.visser@ngh.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
